talktype (0.1.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release (beta)
  * Wayland/GNOME support with daemon-based approach
  * Local Whisper transcription using faster-whisper
  * Clipboard workflow (auto-copy, manual paste)
  * Systemd integration for auto-start
  * GNOME keyboard shortcut integration
  * Convenient CLI commands (talktype command)
  * Bash aliases for daemon management
  * Microphone testing utilities
  * Adjustable speech detection threshold

